Text: Re Oconto Falls Rebox Hedges mtg Cc Gustavos message The referenced meeting is primarily being held to discuss the plan with respect to Oconto Falls Ron Van Den Huevel would also like to discuss the possibility of Enron Providing Risk Management Services to the Rebox Project The Attendees will include Ron Van Den Heuvel Steve Peter Dan Platkowski George Longo FYI The Meeting will take place in conference room If you have any question concerns please call me x Thank you Sarah Reyna Assistant to Jay Boudreaux Forwarded by Sarah ReynaCorpEnron on PM Enron North America Corp From Gustavo Junqueira ECT PM To Sarah NRON cc Raymond CT Peter del CT Bryan CT Finley CT Rodney CT Ana CT Dusty Warren CT Marsha CT Sheri L CT Jay CT Subject Re Oconto Falls Rebox Hedges mtg We are going to be addressing the OFTI sale in the same meeting I beleive that Richard Sanders must be informed about the meeting Sarah NRON PM To Raymond CT Peter del CT Gustavo CT Bryan CT Finley CT Rodney CT cc Ana CT Dusty Warren CT Marsha CT Sheri L CT Jay CT Subject Oconto Falls Rebox Hedges mtg There will be a meeting to discuss Oconto FallsRebox Hedges on Thursday August th pm in conference room Please let me know if you have any questions Thank you Sarah Reyna Assistant to Jay Boudreaux
